custodianMessages.message: Please excuse the "dust" while I work with the Nu Development Team to finalize the reporting pages.

divestments.note: Satisifies the conditions of motion 387e7f6ffc7d69311ac2e1d0ca7cd98d4ecbdea9 and represents a transfer of liquidity from the original grant. This amount is no longer represented in the outstanding grant amount used for calculations.

fundsReserve.notes: Adjustment of active liquidity on the NBT/BTC pair to protect grant funds devaluation losses
fundsReserve.source: Liquidity adjustment from CCEDK NBT/BTC market

fundsReserve.notes: Now that coin control has been included, I moved the grant's reserve funds to unique addresses. It will be easier to keep track of incoming and outgoing transactions. This also allows me to split the reserve into multiple blocks for enhanced security.
